{"tid":1330090,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美發行商發起捐助眾籌 希望粉絲支持京阿尼度過難關","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:47:43.000Z","uid":75050,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7b45989e8835e892c22564deaf2663a3b6be54","tid":1330090,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2382172032053304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2382172032053304&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=cd5f0d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2382172032053304</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2faajd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2faajd.png&h=d43673af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】歐美發行商發起捐助眾籌 希望粉絲支持京阿尼度過難關</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  今天（18號），ACG界元老《京都動畫》（Kyoto Animation）總部突然遭遇罪犯惡意放火，死傷眾多引發社會強烈關注，無數粉絲紛紛聲援。根據最新消息，目前京阿尼（Kyo-Ani）作品的歐美合作發行商Sentai Filmworks已經在網上發起對京阿尼的捐助眾籌。<br />\n<br />\n  從目前的籌款情況來看，<strong><ins>粉絲們在2小時內已經為京阿尼籌集了84809美元，眾籌參與人數達到2445人，而此次眾籌目標金額為50萬美元。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n目前眾籌捐助者們也在該網站頁面留下了自己的想法：<br />\n<br />\n🙏&ldquo;京阿尼一直是，也永遠是超棒的動畫工作室，我會一直支持他們。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n🙏&ldquo;今天的事情糟透了，我想為受害者的家人祈福。京阿尼一直是我心中最好的動畫工作室！永遠愛你們！也永遠支持你們！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n🙏&ldquo;京阿尼為推出了很多我所喜愛的動畫作品，正是因為有了你們的作品，我才不會想著自我傷害。對此，我表示非常感激。對於今天發生的一切，我感到非常心痛。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n🙏&ldquo;我很清楚地知道這點錢並不能讓那些失去生命的人死而復生，但是我希望這點捐助能夠幫助到逝者的家人，也希望此次籌款能讓京阿尼早日恢復。現在，我正在聽《Air》作品中的著名歌曲《鳥之詩》，希望能藉此平定一下自己的心緒。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  京阿尼從2003年開始獨立製作動畫，曾給無數愛好者帶來《涼宮春日》系列、《境界的彼方》、《日常》、《CLANNAD》系列、《幸運星》、《冰菓》、《玉子市場》等作品。希望京阿尼公司能夠平安度過此次劫難。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>眾籌地址連結:</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-kyoani-heal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-kyoani-heal&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=64db9e31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-kyoani-heal</a>"},{"pid":"4b61f1cd3502108a11ec0b9ac93e75d70753734c","tid":1330090,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e53e2a3817d3f99d5737f0d35c191455dfbdd992","tid":1330090,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b61f1cd3502108a11ec0b9ac93e75d70753734c","tid":1330090,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"屌睇錯歐盟以為講譴責果啲<br />\n我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802f5602ae84b5ff2da54cd02323ca8008d8a220","tid":1330090,"uid":151389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"建議等官方交待咗先<br />\n想支持可以去官網買住畫先"},{"pid":"7df0a167d892c254740f5f124bdf880a60b2e202","tid":1330090,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"802f5602ae84b5ff2da54cd02323ca8008d8a220","tid":1330090,"uid":151389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"建議等官方交待咗先<br />\n想支持可以去官網買住畫先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"而家已經34萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdffaacb82872f0d9af6d018655b631766a317c","tid":1330090,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802f5602ae84b5ff2da54cd02323ca8008d8a220","tid":1330090,"uid":151389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"建議等官方交待咗先<br />\n想支持可以去官網買住畫先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"8efce9